<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Agdasima:wght@400;700&family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@11/swiper-bundle.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.css" />
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/script.js"></script>
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <div class="logo_and_name">
            <div class="logo">
                <img src="/assets/gog_logo.png" alt="GOG logo" srcset="">
            </div>
            <div class="church_name">
                <h1>Generals of Grace</h1>
            </div>
        </div>
            

        <div class="menu">
            <ul>
                <li>Home</li>
                <li>About</li>
                <li>Sermons</li>
                <li id="live">Live <div id="live-dot"></div></li>
                <li>Branches</li>
                <li>Testimonies</li>
                <li>Partnership</li>
                <li>Contact Us</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero_section">
    <!-- Hero Section HTML -->
        <div class="swiper-container hero-section">
            <div class="swiper-wrapper">
                <!-- Slide 1 -->
                <div class="swiper-slide slide-img-1">
                    <div class="slide-content">
                        <h1>Welcome to Generals of Grace</h1>
                        <p>A Portal of Encounters, Empowerment, and Transformation</p>
                        <div class="button-div">
                            <a href="#about" class="button">Learn More</a>
                        </div>
                        
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Slide 2 -->
                <div class="swiper-slide slide-img-2">
                    <div class="slide-content">
                        <h1>Empowering Kingdom Generals</h1>
                        <p>Anointed and Equipped to Impact the World</p>
                        <div class="button-div">
                            <a href="#ministries" class="button">Discover Our Mission</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Slide 3 -->
                <div class="swiper-slide slide-img-3">
                    <div class="slide-content">
                        <h1>Experience Divine Encounters</h1>
                        <p>Join Us for Worship and Be Transformed</p>
                        <div class="button-div">
                            <a href="#events" class="button">Join Us</a>
                        </div>
                        
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Swiper Pagination -->
            <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- About us section -->
    <div class="about-us_section">
        <div class="title">
            <h1>Who We Are</h1>    
            <div class="underline">
                <div class="underline-line"></div>
                <div class="underline-dot"></div>
                <div class="underline-line"></div>
            </div>        
        </div>

        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="about-content-img">
                <img src="/assets/image-13.jpg" alt="" srcset="">
            </div>
            <div class="about-content-text-and-cta">
                <div class="about-content-text">
                    <p>Generals of Grace (GOG) is more than a church—it’s a portal of divine encounters where lives are transformed and destinies are unlocked. At GOG, we are a family of passionate believers—young people, families, and leaders—who are empowered by God’s anointing to impact every sphere of life. Our mission is to raise and equip Kingdom generals—men and women who are called to carry the light of God into the world, overcoming darkness and bringing transformation to their communities, workplaces, and nations.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="button">Learn More</div>
            </div>
           
            
        </div>
    </div>    
    <div class="our_mission">
        <div class="title">
            <h1>Our Mission</h1>
            <div class="underline">
                <div class="underline-line"></div>
                <div class="underline-dot"></div>
                <div class="underline-line"></div>
            </div>              
        </div>


        <div class="our_mission-content">
            
            <div class="our_mission-content-text">
                <p>At Generals of Grace (GOG), our mission is to ignite an unquenchable hunger and passion for God in the hearts of men. We are committed to stirring a deep desire for divine encounters, empowering believers to rise up as kingdom generals, and equipping them with spiritual authority to dispel every work of darkness. Through anointed worship, powerful teachings, and life-changing services, we cultivate an atmosphere where lives are transformed and destinies are unleashed to take over the systems of the earth.</p>
            </div>   
            <div class="our_mission-content-img">
                <img src="/assets/image-4.jpeg" alt="" srcset="">
            </div>            
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonies">
        <div class="title">
            <h1>Testimonies</h1>
            <div class="underline">
                <div class="underline-line"></div>
                <div class="underline-dot"></div>
                <div class="underline-line"></div>
            </div> 
        </div>

        <div class="testimonies-content">
            <div class="testimonies-content-each">
                <div class="testimonies-content-each-img">
                    <img src="/assets/testimony-pic1.jpg" alt="" srcset="">
                </div>
                <div class="testimonies-content-each-text">
                    <div class="testimonies-content-each-text-testimony">
                        <p>After attending GOG’s encounter service, my life was never the same. I received clarity and direction for my future. God has opened doors for me in ways I never imagined!</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimonies-content-each-text-testifier">
                        <p>Adebayo A., Abuja</p>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
    

    <script>
        var swiper = new Swiper('.swiper-container', {
        loop: true, // Enables continuous loop
        autoplay: {
            delay: 4000, // Auto-slide every 3 seconds
            disableOnInteraction: false,
        },
        pagination: {
            el: '.swiper-pagination',
            clickable: true,
        },
        effect: 'fade', // Optional for a fading transition effect
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>